.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-6::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: gospel, folk, techno, funk
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: ice-hockey, weightlifting, cricket, badminton
1. the person who's sport is cricket is on the right of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
2. the fan of funk is the person who's sport is cricket##1
3. the fan of funk is on the far right##1
4. the fan of folk is the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
5. the fan of techno is between the fan of gospel and the fan of folk##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |     3     |   4    |
| Music-Genre   | folk     | techno           | gospel | funk  |
| Sport         | ice-hockey | badminton | weightlifting   | cricket |

