.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-7::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: country, classical, salsa, dubstep
The people use 4 different means of transport: taxi, quad-bike, boat, subway
1. the fan of classical is the person driving the taxi##1
2. the person driving the boat is on the left of the person driving the taxi##1
3. the person driving the subway is on the right of the fan of country##1
4. the person driving the quad-bike is on the left of the person driving the subway##1
5. the fan of country is between the person driving the taxi and the fan of salsa##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2    |     3      |     4      |
| Music-Genre   | dubstep   | classical | country | salsa      |
| Transport     | boat | taxi    | quad-bike  | subway |

