.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-10::.
There 4 different types of food: zucchini, radish, eggplant, pepper
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: golf, handball, surfing, climbing
1. the person who's sport is handball is on the right of the person eating pepper##1
2. the person who's sport is surfing is on the right of the person eating eggplant##1
3. the person eating zucchini is on the right of the person eating radish##1
4. the person who's sport is surfing is on the right of the person who's sport is handball##1
5. the person who's sport is handball is between the person eating radish and the person who's sport is climbing##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |     2      |    3     |    4     |
| Food    | pepper   | eggplant      | radish   | zucchini  |
| Sport   | climbing | handball | surfing | golf |

