.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-11::.
There 4 different types of food: spinach, radish, kiwi, grapefruit
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: western, comedy, family, epic
1. the person watching epic movies is on the right of the person watching comedy movies##1
2. the person eating radish is between the person eating grapefruit and the person eating spinach##2
3. the person watching comedy movies is on the right of the person watching family movies##1
4. the person watching family movies is on the right of the person eating spinach##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |    3    |      4      |
| Food          | spinach     | radish | grapefruit   | kiwi        |
| Movie-Genre   | western | family   | comedy | epic |

