.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-12::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: drawing, sudoku, collecting, fishing
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: country, folk, blues, disco
1. the fan of blues is the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
2. the fan of folk is on the left of the fan of disco##1
3. the fan of country is the person who's hobby is drawing##1
4. the person who's hobby is collecting is the fan of folk##1
5. the fan of country is on the right of the person who's hobby is fishing##1
6. the fan of folk is between the person who's hobby is sudoku and the person who's hobby is fishing##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2    |    3    |     4      |
| Hobby         | sudoku | collecting | fishing | drawing |
| Music-Genre   | blues          | folk     | disco  | country     |

