2. the lawyer is between the person watching romance movies and the electrician##2
3. the person watching zombie movies is on the far right##1
4. the electrician is on the left of the person watching musical movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |       2        |    3     |     4     |
| Job           | electrician | lawyer | firefighter | freelancer     |
| Movie-Genre   | thriller   | musical    | romance   | zombie |

