3. the owner of the mouse is between the owner of the bird and the argentine##2
4. the owner of the snake is the owner of the snake##1
5. the owner of the snake is on the right of the owner of the cat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |    3     |     4     |
| Nationality   | polish | argentine | indonesian | thai |
| Pet           | cat  | snake  | mouse | bird      |

