.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-20::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: hiking, chess, video-games, drawing
4 different pets are kept: lizard, frog, bird, turtle
1. the owner of the frog is on the far left##1
2. the person who's hobby is hiking is between the owner of the lizard and the person who's hobby is drawing##2
3. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the left of the person who's hobby is hiking##1
4. the person who's hobby is chess is on the far right##1
5. the person who's hobby is chess is on the right of the owner of the bird##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2      |     3      |    4    |
| Hobby   | video-games    | drawing     | hiking | chess |
| Pet     | frog | turtle | bird       | lizard     |

 